decimals().details: Number of decimals used for fees.

getCreator(uint256).details: Returns the creator of the `tokenId` token.

params.tokenId: NFT ID. NOTE: The Autentica Marketplace smart contract supports royalties, so in order for the creator to be paid, we need to know who created the token and that information must stay the same even if the person who owns the token changes.

getInvestor(uint256).details: Returns the investor of the `tokenId` token.
